  "detailed_description": "<strong>Tech Shop Simulator: Manage Your Own Tech Store!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/c83ae1bbf47225aa7fe8c73914484f96.avif?t=1746898024\" width=400 height=293 /></span><br><br>Are you ready to manage and develop your dream technology store? Tech Shop Simulator offers you the opportunity to establish and run your own technology shop<br><br><strong>Product Procurement</strong><br>Order products from the in-game computer.Receive the products, organize your storage, and arrange them on shelves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/6c3ff801bafcc484384723046b2426f0.poster.avif?t=1746898024\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/6c3ff801bafcc484384723046b2426f0.webm?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/6c3ff801bafcc484384723046b2426f0.mp4?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/95a40365d57eebfa8c3046ebaeec96f8.poster.avif?t=1746898024\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/95a40365d57eebfa8c3046ebaeec96f8.webm?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/95a40365d57eebfa8c3046ebaeec96f8.mp4?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/c37a6609ec30e76005a2f9243b780c04.poster.avif?t=1746898024\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/c37a6609ec30e76005a2f9243b780c04.webm?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/c37a6609ec30e76005a2f9243b780c04.mp4?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Checkout</strong><br>Scan the products, accept payment via customer's credit card or cash and don't forget to give back change for cash transactions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/7137a185545d719cdc8d2af818a1173c.poster.avif?t=1746898024\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/7137a185545d719cdc8d2af818a1173c.webm?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/7137a185545d719cdc8d2af818a1173c.mp4?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Free Market</strong><br>Sell products at your desired price, while considering customer satisfaction<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/f38dc3b24d7df3eb4fcbc5f85de2f58e.poster.avif?t=1746898024\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/f38dc3b24d7df3eb4fcbc5f85de2f58e.webm?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/f38dc3b24d7df3eb4fcbc5f85de2f58e.mp4?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Growth</strong><br>As your profits increase, expand your store and make upgrades using the in-game computer.\"The foundation of growth lies in investing in yourself\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/2296258fbac4fca34d29ac2c18a5d953.poster.avif?t=1746898024\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/2296258fbac4fca34d29ac2c18a5d953.webm?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918270/extras/2296258fbac4fca34d29ac2c18a5d953.mp4?t=1746898024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
